                }
            ],
            "ref_spans": [],
            "section": "SPECIAL ISSUE ARTICLES"
        },
        {
            "text": "With the ongoing opioid crisis and COVID-19 pandemic, chronic pain has become an especially serious public health concern. As the articles in this special issue demonstrate, understanding and leveraging the placebo effect may play an important role in addressing pain.",
